{"title":"Continuum. Diagnóstico y manejo del Ictus cardioembolico-2025","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/Continuum. Diagnóstico y manejo del Ictus cardioembolico-2025.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Diagnóstico y manejo\\Ndel Ictus cardioembolico","guid":"M1keMjNJGVJW2GVPz0mzCw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"General ","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1️⃣ Introducción","guid":"KvsVntVp3NUzdHlQ7eLNdw","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"▶️ Prevalencia: ~30% de los ictus isquémicos.","guid":"jZtEoWXahmgRuJRiLFss1Q","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"▶️ Factores\\Nde riesgo:","guid":"HHDDp7vQ6LfCYrrNHV4rXA","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Alta probabilidad: FA, endocarditis, trombo ventricular izq.","guid":"LeezZZYKOC7pG9bKc8YQTA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Menor probabilidad: FOP.","guid":"9Fm-W8_qGQ-OFe4Ws-Xkcw","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"2","text":"▶️ Prevención\\Nsecundaria:","guid":"Rl3eNkObECyd1SLc3OxcYg","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• ⬆ Identificación del mecanismo del ictus.","guid":"zLx1K8FslCxCPPjGgM5tMQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• ⬆ Control de factores de riesgo.","guid":"I8RYcQpFe9c2lU0hHJgxHQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"2️⃣ Evaluación del Paciente con\\NSospecha de Ictus Cardioembólico","guid":"x809AsIYN_AkMoj0Bw6T8g","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"▶️ Hallazgos iniciales:","guid":"aiLnJduM3sj2fM-gbn1Wwg","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Infarto embólico en imagen","guid":"2PNoW9wzdQyGchPR8zp1Uw","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Sin fuente cardíaca evidente","guid":"3k0zS12D1jrZ96cKC1TYPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"▶️ Pruebas\\Ndiagnósticas:","guid":"9nIAPXvNh7wlSgiqFIXpVQ","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• Ecocardiografía transesofágica → Identifica trombos, tumores, FOP.","guid":"tTu6nBTtYVvTjyPAaDxW0A","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Monitorización cardíaca prolongada → Detecta FA paroxística.","guid":"Q9QiwDwVVLh6ZHVFKKJNKw","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"• Otras pruebas → Detección de miocardiopatías subyacentes.","guid":"kd3e1q78GY7sVxvUj-5CDw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"1","text":"3️⃣ Fibrilación Auricular (FA) y\\NIctus Cardioembólico","guid":"HuDqNo5X7rv8kQd2TfMAGA","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"▶️ Prevalencia: 2% de la población, ⬆ con la edad.","guid":"C8FtFyrOSuanmC0BmAUWxA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"▶️ Clasificación:","guid":"GQc-PeOOAXjm5DbJHzcvFA","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• FA valvular → Con estenosis mitral moderada-severa o prótesis mecánica.","guid":"g22-zHUbNY-s12kCg_xDUg","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"• FA no valvular → Sin los criterios anteriores.","guid":"vByTz_Nkl2I8ME0yd3jLhQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"18","text":"▶️ Estratificación\\Ndel Riesgo:","guid":"lBuDWANLpLfa_6V__PN-HA","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• CHADS₂ (IC, HTA, ≥75a, DM, ictus/AIT)","guid":"w9Ss5wnyub8Ric_Y9lAKMw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• CHA₂DS₂-VASc (+ enfermedad vascular, 65-74a, sexo femenino)","guid":"CGeeI7bsgtiMnGcDT6O2eg","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"18","text":"▶️ Prevención\\Nsecundaria:","guid":"1YvBGGRE8kCjIme93ZgJPA","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• ⬆ Warfarina > AAS para prevenir ictus.","guid":"Ctr8tONSJflwKPhx3y0fHg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Anticoagulantes orales directos (DOACs) ⬇ hemorragia intracraneal vs. warfarina.","guid":"eYbP44ZMhqcSOr8KudyPYA","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"18","text":"▶️ Oclusión de la Orejuela\\NAuricular Izquierda:","guid":"opb7QNtAVsS8RMhsRYdjLQ","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Alternativa a anticoagulación en px con alto riesgo hemorrágico.","guid":"tu3SpsK_ehoL-lfXAFmhhA","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"• Dispositivos: WATCHMAN, Amulet.","guid":"fxkSZPvvL4VBaDeN0lcGSQ","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"• En estudio: CHAMPION-AF, CATALYST.","guid":"SwYuIkEhAkZtpzkjoeepOw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"1","text":"4️⃣ Otras Causas\\NCardioembólicas","guid":"HoGsP47vMj52Lkoc7ebGhw","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"🔹 Atriopatía","guid":"KX8W2jNEAocGzJAo71SvtA","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"▶️ Cambios estructurales y eléctricos en la aurícula izquierda ⬆ riesgo de ictus.","guid":"STlsXCy5D1Y9aGrtxaidfA","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"🔹 Foramen Oval\\NPermeable (FOP)","guid":"TcfiU4utdHEd5s_-9wJsNg","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"▶️ Riesgo relativo en <60a con ictus criptogénico.","guid":"2uXn2FxLyCyAb9kSng8K8Q","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"▶️ Opciones: cierre percutáneo vs. manejo médico.","guid":"-RxbtQ_1JQNFEAiXDS-JSg","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"33","text":"🔹 Miocardiopatía y Disfunción Ventricular Izquierda","guid":"eS6LnTfMCp-tkAOQYFLRpA","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"▶️ FEVI reducida ⬆ tromboembolismo → Indicación de anticoagulación.","guid":"XKlMoHipQx0s4mtjHGYLlg","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"33","text":"🔹 Infarto Agudo de\\NMiocardio (IAM)","guid":"7Y7o3Ys3pLc4rsqbX5bw6A","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"▶️ Mayor riesgo en IAM con trombo mural.","guid":"nGDFpUkP43LuTz1jW4NkPw","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"▶️ Manejo: anticoagulación + antiagregación.","guid":"YrIpU22HyuxtuSNqsUjq2g","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"33","text":"🔹 Enfermedad\\NValvular","guid":"Gln0Js2KzwVVEVjLMOLBog","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"▶️ Estenosis mitral → FA secundaria, ⬆ riesgo embólico.","guid":"vkFlssF2np1H2AdwDzr-gQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"▶️ Endocarditis → Vegetaciones sépticas embolizantes.","guid":"c7ZH2vx9HkMAD3GyhgEX1g","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"33","text":"🔹 Tumores\\NCardíacos","guid":"wZUAVGRtj8lqIaMGntDzxw","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"▶️ Mixoma auricular → Fuente embólica frecuente.","guid":"4x_Kk4Jx9Yk7tNJ5XIGvUg","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"▶️ Manejo: cirugía.","guid":"rzsFloEd4dtf0ZxwgYl8Zw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"1","text":"5️⃣ Ictus Cardioembólico\\Ny Anticoagulación","guid":"_9LOvPEtH01F61erdQ58bw","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"▶️ Inicio de Anticoagulación\\Ntras Ictus Agudo","guid":"SZ5L7Sga5mCxI_REEZXd0Q","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Heparina o HBPM NO recomendadas → ⬆ hemorragia.","guid":"-zjI75tHSgbrGwj4Hqo3OA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"• DOACs preferidos sobre warfarina.","guid":"0xpROqbVgWl94w8_GIzmRw","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"▶️ Tiempo\\Nde inicio:","guid":"gbOhjH4YfcaZQmjRFwJ_NA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• Ictus leve → 0-3 días.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"• Ictus moderado → 4-14 días.","guid":"Mwday_cuwl0fCeDOc2d_-Q","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"• Ictus grave → >14 días.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"50","text":"▶️ Px con ictus a pesar\\Nde anticoagulación:","guid":"ViUfNkB0NDHHgu9gpaEF4Q","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• Evaluar adherencia y niveles plasmáticos.","guid":"ysruV8m3osT_wlfXrqQ7OA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"• Considerar mecanismos alternativos (aterosclerosis, microangiopatía).","guid":"i4O1NDx-ZtkIgvEfn0vTyQ","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"• Opciones: cambio de anticoagulante, cierre de orejuela.","guid":"ZUteHNwbG6w0UHM3LEpSFA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"1","text":"6️⃣ Consideraciones en Px con\\NAlto Riesgo Hemorrágico","guid":"DfePyuv5wHOUc2T5DUdI0A","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"▶️ Historia de Hemorragia\\NIntracraneal (HIC)","guid":"r06XqnENay5gJ8g6dqfpMA","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"• Reanudar anticoagulación en px seleccionados.","guid":"qF1oXegrodkiZthuiETRcA","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"• Ensayos en curso: ASPIRE, ENRICH-AF.","guid":"LRVh5OaftW2DnNoG-a_kHQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"▶️ Hemorragia\\NExtracraneal","guid":"vK8_3Iiebj6WgcLlS5U8hg","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• Anticoagulación tras tratamiento\\Ndefinitivo del sangrado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"• Oclusión de orejuela en px con\\Nhemorragia recurrente.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"0","text":"4️⃣ Atriopatía y Riesgo de\\NIctus Cardioembólico","guid":"iyiQ5TV-3oFTvvVd-tZ_4A","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"▶️ Definición: Disfunción auricular sin FA evidente, pero con riesgo tromboembólico.","guid":"kB1tfLrc8EWHhityEGIJbg","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"🔹 Evidencia de Atriopatía\\Ncomo Factor de Riesgo","guid":"VLN59PWZfvwnR8nOXDpKeA","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"▶️ FA y accidente cerebrovascular (ACV) no siempre tienen relación temporal.","guid":"WBagS1gKayqYZFTHi7DlWw","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"▶️ Atriopatía = sustrato patológico para la formación de trombos.","guid":"H8u-vP_luAjdZLGqgg6tPg","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"71","text":"▶️ Biomarcadores\\Nde riesgo:","guid":"QmzCRmsetEzPVrEPdrxNNQ","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"• ⬆ Tamaño aurícula izquierda (≥4.6 cm).","guid":"XHwW4XMtHuRqJC-noswSCQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"• ⬆ Fuerza terminal de la onda P en V1.","guid":"np-AFyMSvUBXkQnFSL8Y7Q","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"• ⬆ NT-proBNP (>250 pg/mL o >750 pg/mL en WARSS).","guid":"W8_xsd1UWnEw2Kmxk8mYcg","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"74","text":"• ⬆ Fibrosis auricular.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"69","text":"🔹 Biología de la Orejuela Auricular Izquierda (OAI)\\Ny Tromboembolismo","guid":"18zY7jGji3S0g1JDZEvB1Q","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"▶️ Factores\\Nde riesgo:","guid":"KXZcAAozsKTbfrUOzlKsEA","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Morfología de alto riesgo.","guid":"AGY3GyqadqZuA33UedtpdQ","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"• ↓ Velocidad de flujo (<0.2 cm/s).","guid":"bY2Y9AivPR4zREQcLezOWQ","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"• Fibrosis en OAI.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"79","text":"▶️ Algunos px sin FA detectada pueden desarrollar trombos en la OAI.","guid":"ewRhpB1EvFsDEeVrNCffQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"69","text":"🔹 Evidencia sobre\\NAnticoagulación en Atriopatía","guid":"IH9q77vdjEgxRHmhcavLjA","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"▶️ Post-hoc de\\Nensayos clínicos:","guid":"LNApPlrcPQStVJEB_cocIQ","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"• WARSS: Warfarina mejor que AAS en px con NT-proBNP >750 pg/mL.","guid":"zzhkvwjNcpJcGeSYQCCOzw","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"• NAVIGATE-ESUS: Rivaroxabán mejor que AAS en px con AI >4.6 cm.","guid":"JYLzVMB4ocVMDmFIDmglCg","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"▶️ Hallazgos sugieren que algunos px con atriopatía pueden beneficiarse de anticoagulación.","guid":"S0Y_WBtXNqITBkUhXNJU8A","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"▶️ Pero: FA oculta podría explicar beneficio → falta evidencia definitiva.","guid":"-eJ0UVxqtbMojsnU3tbQ3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"69","text":"🔹 Ensayos\\NClínicos en Curso","guid":"vWHvguQ2EClziJQMNRRs9A","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"▶️ ATTICUS (Apixabán vs. AAS en ESUS\\Ncon criterios de tromboembolismo cardíaco).","guid":"ekPG8wcL0muZBkrEJ5KtDQ","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"• Suspendido por futilidad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"• 23% de px desarrollaron FA detectada.","guid":"uSZuypdD7LSYe_fXORtSVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"▶️ ARCADIA (Apixabán vs. AAS en\\Nictus criptogénico con atriopatía).","guid":"o1SQG_DDPlGWUka0-o34mA","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• Criterios:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• AI ≥3 cm/m²","guid":"I06-D8habXbXSgTY6gcOWA","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"• NT-proBNP >250 pg/mL","guid":"RiJyqZviBBQDSd9wQW5_Mg","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"• P-terminal en V1 ≥5000 μV × ms","guid":"dFdABOzNY9S67jaCYUZ77A","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"95","text":"• En curso → aclarará si la anticoagulación es efectiva en atriopatía sin FA.","guid":"81nHWvJxwKDf-jGCkKvcMA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"69","text":"🔹 Conclusión","guid":"ADhgUIzvakUaO7SEwULDGQ","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"▶️ Atriopatía = posible causa de ictus cardioembólico sin FA diagnosticada.","guid":"Z2SaHEWrFzMHgNU8Y_dkJA","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"▶️ Biomarcadores pueden identificar px de alto riesgo.","guid":"HOtd0UwkWQYRm9VxQMcz5g","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"▶️ Evidencia actual sugiere posible beneficio de anticoagulación, pero falta confirmación en ensayos controlados.","guid":"zaGUsnyWj15iz-QoiYcMbA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"0","text":"5️⃣ Foramen Oval Permeable\\N(FOP) e Ictus Cardioembólico","guid":"422drDBD1tJ0jqgTS1IynQ","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"▶️ Definición: Defecto septal congénito presente en ~25% de la población.","guid":"R0VOgxLo3BaimOonTuvYrg","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"▶️ Mecanismo: Cortocircuito derecha-izquierda → embolismo paradójico.","guid":"Jni-RjR3a1EzHUcmbXHZiA","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"▶️ Diagnóstico:","guid":"Ikuwjt5CWn_a4eiUA1UEmg","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Estudio de burbujas → Doppler transcraneal (mayor sensibilidad)\\No ecocardiografía transesofágica (visualización directa).","guid":"Dg26C4o1_kWhmJmlA1nv3A","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"• Clasificación\\Ndel shunt:","guid":"lneXf5cSHYtfEfB2YfZxqA","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"• Pequeño: 3-10 burbujas.","guid":"uVPZlGjFEtJSEFKaM0j-Ig","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"• Mediano: 10-20 burbujas.","guid":"TzQGdon3zcAzM8eeDlyOZA","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"110","text":"• Grande: >20 burbujas.","guid":"aNXJg4V_hg9UXXcy4ovv2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"108","text":"• Asociaciones de alto riesgo: Aneurisma del septo auricular.","guid":"SpiEaLspcTSS_55lMc_Kjg","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"105","text":"🔹 FOP y\\NRiesgo de Ictus","guid":"pTSKWnHsy-0L9Y_Va2Hgew","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"▶️ Asociación con ictus criptogénico.","guid":"l-0_aPE2q5cd0HvATVuGMw","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"▶️ Mecanismos\\Npostulados:","guid":"5PzAQ0MhxH2v6XG1WGiE9Q","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"• Embolismo paradójico → Trombosis venosa profunda.","guid":"_HMm6iZNJ6yiSELi1duflg","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"• Trombosis in situ en el FOP.","guid":"cjw8boO9UDtAFWWu6YO-Sw","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"115","text":"▶️ Determinación\\Nde causalidad:","guid":"eR8EuJGLtfeKXq4SvHrLiA","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"• RoPE Score (Riesgo de\\NEmbolismo Paradoxal):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• PFO patogénico: RoPE 9-10 → 2% recurrencia a 2 años.","guid":"YpWLbQLmSVvFKtmhsgFqrQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• PFO incidental: RoPE 0-2 → 20% recurrencia a 2 años.","guid":"RdoAAwl58W0qFtpllaDhhA","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"120","text":"• Clasificación PASCAL → Evalúa características de alto riesgo (shunt grande, aneurisma septal).","guid":"DQyKKbb7FMCzHJw7KzGSrg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"105","text":"🔹 Tratamiento del FOP\\Nen Ictus Isquémico","guid":"b2qNgCenQ6t6BsVpjCnt4Q","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"▶️ Opciones\\Nterapéuticas:","guid":"PVagwFKJV2waOYB5uBFIEA","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"• Antitrombóticos → AAS o anticoagulación (si hay TVP).","guid":"MR4-bNkwUHMAwMo-vRrYkQ","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"• Cierre percutáneo en casos seleccionados.","guid":"iS59aKcim49gPNvBBLhW3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"🔸 Evidencia sobre\\NAntitrombóticos","guid":"tL0HmGRSfxztbPaxgbTUnA","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"▶️ PICSS (WARSS-subestudio) → Warfarina = AAS en px con FOP.","guid":"4ryJ6eMacUxFUvHHPjSPXg","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"▶️ NAVIGATE-ESUS /\\NRESPECT-ESUS:","guid":"N7Z0xOGNNiagg-ng-CeacA","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"• Rivaroxabán vs. AAS → Similar riesgo de ictus recurrente.","guid":"wXKSYjKxh7Y0HgynCPmLCA","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"• Dabigatrán vs. AAS → Similar riesgo de ictus y sangrado.","guid":"UAq0IUB8_IzTtQWHwEEGEQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"129","text":"▶️ Meta-análisis de 4 ensayos → AAS = anticoagulantes en prevención secundaria.","guid":"XZm33FlAx57j2o9sfUmcyA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"105","text":"🔹 Cierre del FOP:\\NEvidencia Clínica","guid":"574sNs8Rn3vX2rFasRVRgA","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"▶️ Ensayos iniciales\\N(CLOSURE, PC, RESPECT):","guid":"KBmhpsA_TQ1q3yjfmXRANg","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"• No mostraron beneficio claro del cierre vs. terapia médica.","guid":"xkdlolN6eGwaujs52a8T2w","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"▶️ Ensayos recientes (CLOSE,\\NREDUCE, DEFENSE-PFO):","guid":"ilAYDR30obuqQahFmVKfOA","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• ⬆ Beneficio del cierre en px con FOP de alto riesgo.","guid":"ypZ5Lu9cS4WsgfpY8gpQAA","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"• ⬆ Riesgo de FA post-cierre.","guid":"LAGf1nPMTpOtd_YyYh-yvA","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"135","text":"▶️ Meta-análisis\\Nde 6 ensayos:","guid":"3dhXno5JMGHEtJz4JLSh5Q","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"• RoPE ≥7 → HR 0.21 (p < .02) → Mayor beneficio del cierre.","guid":"n8mx_Xrc3SQ-LTUsxrX9Gw","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"• Clasificación PASCAL “posible/probable” → Mayor beneficio.","guid":"jjU-Kc-YlRrBaKA3N-5i4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"135","text":"▶️ Complicaciones: FA post-procedimiento más frecuente en PASCAL “unlikely”.","guid":"Shy6Xcz7YX9lNrjRf_47BA","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"105","text":"🔹 Consideraciones\\Nen Px >60 años","guid":"p1IUU0bPm4qwTKO9MTSt4g","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"▶️ No hay evidencia clara de beneficio del cierre en este grupo.","guid":"smnlVmyrhAXN8lXW2VSCjA","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"▶️ Cierre podría considerarse\\Nen px seleccionados si:","guid":"Z9jd-cel5MgXAca_fGcmlw","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"• FOP de alto riesgo (shunt grande, aneurisma septal).","guid":"yu2swDZaH4oifWN0itg1_w","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"• Sin otra causa de ictus tras monitoreo ≥30 días.","guid":"OGaxzc6NFJM1NCU-Q48yaQ","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"• Mínimos o nulos factores de riesgo vascular.","guid":"Ng-OxaWWvPMcA3CI0xXWSQ","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"147","text":"• Clasificación PASCAL “posible” o “probable”.","guid":"5zS7nRid2fbAk1s4idocWQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"105","text":"🔹 Conclusión","guid":"Gr7_YNdmEszY-KafRUBoDw","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"▶️ FOP es un hallazgo frecuente, pero no siempre patogénico.","guid":"B_5r81-FftawBBdQvNK0PA","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"▶️ Estratificación del riesgo (RoPE, PASCAL) clave en la decisión terapéutica.","guid":"WAyvlVTbZ9Np3p1DpYLKCQ","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"▶️ Terapia médica (AAS vs. anticoagulación) razonable en la mayoría de los px.","guid":"1xgJgWxzJjewkcyIftBTYg","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"▶️ Cierre percutáneo indicado en px jóvenes con ictus criptogénico y FOP de alto riesgo.","guid":"Yl852XYpH2_qXzWxqxqehg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"0","text":"6️⃣ Ictus Isquémico en el\\NContexto de Enfermedad Aórtica","guid":"vx2HllS1BKoqSBtLw7mD4g","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"▶️ Mecanismo: Embolismo arteria-a-arteria por ateromas del arco aórtico o disección aórtica ascendente.","guid":"ESkqXWWqah_eNZWxHVQIxw","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"🔹 Ateromas del Arco\\NAórtico y Riesgo de Ictus","guid":"YKSgNXVUvt2qiahCvcyb8g","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"▶️ Factores de\\Nalto riesgo:","guid":"60CUU32keaAHgSMx6zsdNw","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"• Ateromas ≥4 mm.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"• Ateromas móviles o ulcerados.","guid":"7jq30GSpoI5Tc52bMFhuQQ","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"160","text":"• Localización en aorta ascendente o arco aórtico.","guid":"YJC1ZoToN6IhNsFcM6MNKA","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"159","text":"▶️ Mayor asociación con ictus criptogénico.","guid":"ziaC1b92JuG5BwzFbCElzg","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"159","text":"▶️ Diagnóstico:","guid":"ZacUFCVuo0SSquK0gKElpg","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"• Ecocardiografía transesofágica → Gold standard para visualizar ateromas.","guid":"EdyMpdQbtsdXk64Gp00zKw","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"• Alternativas no invasivas: Angio-TC, RM cardíaca.","guid":"eiVC6-6WcpSbrFU9IIsMHg","children":[]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"159","text":"🔸 Prevención\\NSecundaria","guid":"sOibxABNRIN0aIhVGiMQCg","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"▶️ Terapia\\Nmédica:","guid":"gbEZT3BSmKS4JKIixMC44Q","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"• Control de factores de riesgo.","guid":"4q6R2IjbMMJsqOBn3T9-Cw","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"• Estatinas de alta intensidad.","guid":"MyDfGKSQuQr8GPEr7O7x-g","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"• Antiagregación plaquetaria → tratamiento preferido.","guid":"tJQiDR9BQz8L3o3_m0Ohxg","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"168","text":"▶️ Evidencia\\N(Ensayo ARCH):","guid":"UtsYimsvvuDK_OSpHFhZig","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"• Warfarina vs. AAS + Clopidogrel → ⬆ eventos isquémicos y hemorrágicos con warfarina.","guid":"QqB1LeBMkqn2rCiv3zclsA","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"• Mortalidad vascular: Warfarina 3.4% vs. DAPT 0% (P = .013).","guid":"IWXOnZCo21AS4HYTi_o2bw","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"168","text":"▶️ DAPT por 30 días en px seleccionados (CHANCE, POINT, THALES).","guid":"wUWkfxFwLPI92-mPCgyavQ","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"168","text":"▶️ Casos excepcionales: Cirugía en ateromas de alto riesgo con ictus recurrente.","guid":"6nkHrcXI0r-uO1Fqpi8BRA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"157","text":"🔹 Disección Aórtica\\NAscendente e Ictus","guid":"GyEAElyUdrwoDb6hcjUppg","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"▶️ Causa rara de ictus con alta mortalidad (~60% sin cirugía).","guid":"5GW5e_QtkAP_42coJaHiuA","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"▶️ Factores de riesgo:","guid":"zEpq1zX6246L-vr6NVXHzQ","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"• Síndromes genéticos: Marfan, Loeys-Dietz, Ehlers-Danlos IV.","guid":"15ZfBYPfhUwg3erJVQXvQQ","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"• Aneurismas familiares de aorta torácica.","guid":"F-4lsY_hgREpRTr277o5wA","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"• Válvula aórtica bicúspide.","guid":"iIdpvwaH6NhB3iIG3OY8Ng","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"178","text":"▶️ Manifestaciones\\Nclínicas:","guid":"tjuKK7lP5b22dcowRs6okQ","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"• Ictus isquémico ± dolor torácico.","guid":"FZ6FpFO9KIfq_4vR3t8rPQ","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"• Síntomas de isquemia de otros órganos.","guid":"Wlj_NRd-IGx4Iv-LFmz1AA","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"178","text":"🔸 Diagnóstico","guid":"pHnfdEQEiJDg3H-9eNrWXw","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"▶️ Hemodinámicamente estable:","guid":"hdxzhcVKOkw60Ba367ucfQ","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"• Angio-TC de aorta → Gold standard.","guid":"YoJ4dpsoJjQuznMYrGULhg","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"▶️ Hemodinámicamente inestable:","guid":"Fc6GJXelykGN3cqZxZICaQ","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"• Ecocardiografía transtorácica/transesofágica → Evalúa válvula aórtica y derrame pericárdico.","guid":"LWGjkT7iLJoE5xIYH69cBA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"178","text":"🔸 Manejo","guid":"VoSfaEqSZ0InyWZ42qCl0Q","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"▶️ Dilema clínico:","guid":"2lolg6m1vTp48Mrayyl7XA","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"• Control estricto de PA → ⬇ progresión de la disección pero ⬇ perfusión cerebral.","guid":"HHmy64np4uQlMdKWwj5CRg","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"• Riesgo de transformación hemorrágica con cirugía aórtica.","guid":"vU3Ky0nKJRIbUmSVsQi76g","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"192","text":"▶️ Manejo quirúrgico:","guid":"MJFhLtwyf5FRYMySo5-Hkw","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"• Reparación quirúrgica urgente → Indicada en todos los px con disección ascendente.","guid":"Y6LQgp-iJja-ylBxoyVlzQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"157","text":"🔹 Conclusión","guid":"zDcWwRCHlySK4tognRKKUQ","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"▶️ Ateromas aórticos = importante fuente embólica en ictus criptogénico.","guid":"TwbTR_22w_1akqWwTFhyaQ","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"▶️ Antiagregación (no anticoagulación) preferida en ateromas del arco aórtico.","guid":"tDgW0uL6h8pglPs_Vnu_YQ","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"▶️ Disección aórtica = emergencia con alta mortalidad → cirugía urgente.","guid":"9-fFGK9OQw-tpEdM1AVchA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"0","text":"7️⃣ Ictus Isquémico en el Contexto de\\NDisfunción Ventricular Izquierda","guid":"aqoOgIc--HGun50CH5mXMA","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"▶️ Mecanismo: Formación de trombo ventricular izquierdo (TVI) → embolismo.","guid":"6TnQZNFHjMqfVYpwAyP2Zg","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"▶️ Mayor riesgo en FEVI ⬇ (<15%) o con antecedente de ictus.","guid":"rmT1miHRj-oYhLw_NiKEgA","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"🔹 Factores de Riesgo en\\NInsuficiencia Cardíaca (IC)\\NSistólica","guid":"S9pg0R6y05j6bWycQBci8w","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"▶️ FEVI <15% → HR 2.13 (p = .012).","guid":"Cp2yvWsSbsfYbuGHGMlMmQ","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"205","text":"▶️ FEVI <30% + antecedente de ictus → HR 2.66 (p < .001).","guid":"TpMkh475D1C_Nk97vG593Q","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"205","text":"▶️ Posibles\\Ncausas embólicas:","guid":"8s-hqy7BneWr5M-nQVBZdw","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"• Trombo en VI → Diagnóstico con Eco-TT con contraste (Perflutren) o RM cardíaca (más sensible).","guid":"FXueSmna8WqsxHgFP7VhTA","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"208","text":"• FA paroxística → Importante realizar monitoreo cardíaco prolongado.","guid":"AzfKsVFtXPiqtx-EysnU4A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"202","text":"🔹 Manejo de TVI en IC\\Ncon FEVI Reducida","guid":"iapVbDf-0iMbAsZ1yqlGLw","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"▶️ Anticoagulación ≥3 meses con warfarina (INR 2-3) hasta resolución del trombo en imagen.","guid":"F0j7di3YMlEzrzB9SkO1Ig","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"▶️ DOACs: Datos limitados en TVI.","guid":"r9kzIYYiAWsmDL8DhuySOQ","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"🔸 Evidencia en Anticoagulación\\N(Ensayo WARCEF)","guid":"-yhL91MybPpEcTBuJLauXw","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"▶️ Pacientes con FEVI ≤35% en ritmo sinusal → Warfarina vs. AAS (325 mg/día).","guid":"W1tojE4zM40za_jL4D0mWQ","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"▶️ Resultados:","guid":"rWbKf1_k-iUgo7VJwNgimQ","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"• ⬇ Ictus isquémico con warfarina (HR 0.52; p < .05).","guid":"qXgeyadLEKQGeUEtnBA0BA","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"• ⬆ Hemorragia intracraneal con warfarina (HR 2.22, no significativo).","guid":"4dC-5C5yoftA53CO-hVTOQ","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"216","text":"• Sin diferencias en mortalidad/ictus combinado (HR 0. 93).","guid":"o8Jj8yuKjLC0nRLkBtuKWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"220","parent":"214","text":"▶️ Consideración de Warfarina: Px con FEVI <30% + ictus previo + buena expectativa de vida.","guid":"Bwx6tm_p2DpeCq7ZRSKcdA","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"214","text":"▶️ Eco-TT de seguimiento → Reevaluar función ventricular tras terapia óptima de IC.","guid":"IwG2QqRF3J69lC7hqz8iMQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"202","text":"🔹 ¿DOACs\\Ncomo Alternativa?","guid":"aOfrH3ZFPndgrdzlL2EPgg","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"▶️ DOACs ⬇ riesgo de HIC vs. Warfarina.","guid":"Au6eagT5s-avKZCuIONL8w","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"▶️ Post-hoc de NAVIGATE-ESUS\\N(Pacientes con FEVI moderada-severa):","guid":"vNN_RFvjtWe1MJwaqnQkbQ","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"• Rivaroxabán vs. AAS → ⬇ riesgo de ictus/embolismo sistémico en px con DVI (HR 0.36).","guid":"o-HMjN9kGWmiCkigo6tj8Q","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"• Sin beneficio en px sin disfunción ventricular (HR 1.16).","guid":"WDQoY0fLSQ1n9kiC61CXqA","children":[]}]},{"id":"227","parent":"222","text":"▶️ Se requieren ensayos clínicos específicos comparando DOACs vs. AAS en px con FEVI ⬇ e ictus.","guid":"XBFOyq5PmCw80PiCZLT_zg","children":[]}]},{"id":"228","parent":"202","text":"🔹 Conclusión","guid":"Ck6kXC39tRHVrLeHIq2AVw","children":[{"id":"229","parent":"228","text":"▶️ Ictus en IC con FEVI ⬇ → Relacionado con TVI o FA paroxística.","guid":"o_RNBrGP7KFFsh589ehaVw","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"228","text":"▶️ Anticoagulación con Warfarina en px con TVI → Mínimo 3 meses.","guid":"9kWTxcnaeAsylKQ9v5u2ow","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"228","text":"▶️ DOACs podrían ser una opción segura, pero falta evidencia robusta.","guid":"-uRJm0mRg2EuGaaKbHapkA","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"228","text":"▶️ Monitoreo cardíaco prolongado para descartar FA en todos los casos.","guid":"6vztUQ9UMw5ZsaSrDcsAfA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"0","text":"8️⃣ Ictus Isquémico en el Contexto de\\NInfarto de Miocardio (IAM)","guid":"_xhLFNTgW0G9vP_ZnvjQVg","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"▶️ Mayor riesgo de ictus tras IAM, especialmente en las primeras 12 semanas.","guid":"yFRZ7BqfidiocHT1YBpg8Q","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"233","text":"▶️ IAM silente también ⬆ riesgo de ictus, sobre todo en ictus no lacunar (HR 2.40).","guid":"22fR170Z_w4DvphLCpQceQ","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"233","text":"🔹 Mecanismos de\\NIctus tras IAM","guid":"R6jNDaQqQ5hVf35qpi3LKg","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"▶️ Trombo ventricular izquierdo (TVI) → Embolismo sistémico.","guid":"JlCfLGJA8HGQ7XWueKNSLg","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"236","text":"▶️ FA paroxística inducida por IAM.","guid":"o9ceHyOBHzJodjkcDCmI6Q","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"236","text":"▶️ Hipercoagulabilidad transitoria en IAM agudo.","guid":"UcSp3wIQs8Kqx_32bm3vNw","children":[]}]},{"id":"240","parent":"233","text":"🔹 Manejo según\\NEscenario Clínico","guid":"X-wG_q4QM1chZVTptb68zA","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"🔸 IAM + Ictus + TVI","guid":"_T__qI2_OXMk0PzE02wutA","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"▶️ Anticoagulación ≥3 meses con warfarina (INR 2-3) hasta resolución del trombo.","guid":"M1md5MNDkQN_adAruehMiA","children":[]}]},{"id":"243","parent":"240","text":"🔸 IAM Anterior con Elevación del ST + Ictus","guid":"wJlEugD7X1IWayLdfFNAgg","children":[{"id":"244","parent":"243","text":"▶️ Considerar warfarina por 3 meses si es seguro (evidencia limitada).","guid":"Vgmxupm-swmerzVgdPNSNQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"245","parent":"240","text":"🔸 IAM sin TVI\\N+ Ictus","guid":"EfayYyVFZEdbCFhtJKF77w","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"▶️ Monitoreo cardíaco prolongado → Descarta FA oculta.","guid":"x7Hn9w-yOq1gVRLAI00nrQ","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"245","text":"▶️ Si FA negativa → Antiagregación (AAS preferido).","guid":"qf8njolS7oE64hx0Nb3Zfw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"248","parent":"233","text":"🔹 ¿DOACs\\Ncomo Alternativa?","guid":"wLCYVHae_dhKf85iKYlUYg","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"▶️ Posible beneficio en IAM sin TVI, pero falta evidencia clínica.","guid":"u77iV7zzBCDjEt14qOSRJg","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"248","text":"▶️ Ensayos clínicos necesarios para comparar DOACs vs. antiagregantes.","guid":"9k2CIYEjqXph7TYPHt8nlg","children":[]}]},{"id":"251","parent":"233","text":"🔹 Conclusión","guid":"WesQHZ9MUbv_xtghfl5aKA","children":[{"id":"252","parent":"251","text":"▶️ IAM reciente es un factor de alto riesgo para ictus.","guid":"KuEWaSj0Gp1V8wnG6XBwfg","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"251","text":"▶️ TVI → Anticoagulación obligatoria ≥3 meses.","guid":"ShFwoNNp5kY7OCD6y9v2zg","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"251","text":"▶️ FA paroxística post-IAM debe descartarse con monitoreo prolongado.","guid":"M0ZavaHlBSa59vOPylhAfw","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"251","text":"▶️ Sin FA ni TVI → Antiagregación.","guid":"ADcDzKNLkNF9mQpSYNIl7w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"256","parent":"0","text":"9️⃣ Ictus Isquémico en el Contexto\\Nde Enfermedad Valvular","guid":"dFxkBBWvXDDAg2yn6vFfnQ","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"▶️ Patologías valvulares\\Nasociadas a ictus:","guid":"Uh8j35kevZXTD_q4UmCXig","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"• Válvulas protésicas (bioprotésicas y mecánicas).","guid":"WXEoJrM0ZwPPCjUSOp156Q","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"• Enfermedad reumática (estenosis mitral).","guid":"dFI7l3LSKWFqFe3N3cBu9g","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"257","text":"• Endocarditis infecciosa y no infecciosa (marántica, Libman-Sacks).","guid":"3dINDLEpIJ7hLpMrSpR5MA","children":[]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"256","text":"🔹 Ictus en Válvulas\\NProtésicas","guid":"_YqMxKYBQ5_JkYvbMylicA","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"▶️ Válvula\\Nbioprotésica","guid":"jphdsXBfB9uiOKSuHy_jQA","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"• Evaluar fallo valvular, trombosis o infección como causa del ictus.","guid":"SUr8nDa_P7jPWQvOdZJs8A","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"262","text":"• Sin FA → Anticoagulación 3-6 meses, luego antiagregación.","guid":"-7g7KUvQ_BQMbYcXfXKmIg","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"262","text":"• Ictus en terapia antiagregante → No hay evidencia clara de cambiar a anticoagulación.","guid":"GBW4WJywSUiCsdlNbDAjug","children":[]}]},{"id":"266","parent":"261","text":"▶️ Válvula\\Nmecánica","guid":"iq8ORNlS_smnj45r4ZU5Ew","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"• Warfarina\\N(INR objetivo):","guid":"MU0_w88Sq8r0fQKh7mkdAA","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"• Válvula aórtica → 2.0-3.0.","guid":"IlVWXrbktzzwaMxYEcIXPQ","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"267","text":"• Válvula mitral → 2.5-3.5.","guid":"7y_ayqzSBpbT28zzNkQzTA","children":[]}]},{"id":"270","parent":"266","text":"• Añadir AAS en px con bajo riesgo hemorrágico/aterosclerosis.","guid":"_PFqLCjqE8k-8ryIwk3oTw","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"266","text":"• DOACs NO recomendados (Ensayo RE-ALIGN: ⬆ eventos tromboembólicos y hemorrágicos).","guid":"Z8W6kzetImf_vpdgpWFqmQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"272","parent":"256","text":"🔹 Ictus en Enfermedad\\NValvular Reumática","guid":"wvYPqtvZkY7BS5S4-MkzsA","children":[{"id":"273","parent":"272","text":"▶️ Principal mecanismo: FA secundaria a estenosis mitral reumática.","guid":"mjM5_-8Dj-cM31ABMiCZsg","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"272","text":"▶️ Diagnóstico: Excluir otras causas de ictus (aterosclerosis, microangiopatía).","guid":"zS_h8wCDJntuUnsWNfT8iA","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"272","text":"▶️ Manejo según\\Npresencia de FA:","guid":"mbzBAFh3naCvh_5KWR-09w","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"• Con FA + estenosis mitral moderada-severa → Warfarina preferida.","guid":"TqMG8q836FbwTgKW_7fWBQ","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"• Con FA sin estenosis mitral severa → DOACs o warfarina.","guid":"VWZyh35NFVx6g8xk-zAR4Q","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"• Sin FA → No hay evidencia de beneficio con anticoagulación.","guid":"3SYtj2tlnzB8lLmdASKuAQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"279","parent":"256","text":"🔹 Ictus en Endocarditis\\N(Infecciosa y No Infecciosa)","guid":"E5B-gA4e_eD2q8RKlTT_bQ","children":[{"id":"280","parent":"279","text":"▶️ Endocarditis\\Ninfecciosa (aórtica o\\Nmitral)","guid":"MvYCfnicMmltBtKCRCxBuQ","children":[{"id":"281","parent":"280","text":"• ⬆ Riesgo de ictus 4 meses antes - 5 meses después del diagnóstico.","guid":"s7JaD5PIKHvEPY0HcI4N0g","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"280","text":"• Sospechar en px con bacteriemia persistente (Criterios de Duke).","guid":"fSd3QCI2-4irqn17tijQWA","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"280","text":"• Diagnóstico: Eco-TE (vegetaciones valvulares).","guid":"DPIWwYOq_BKk_NO-KFxnAg","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"280","text":"• Neuroimagen:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"• Infecciosa → Puede mostrar cualquier patrón de infarto.","guid":"t5o2fAxNML1pZalhGNJoFA","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"284","text":"• Marántica (no infecciosa) → Lesiones diseminadas y puntiformes.","guid":"OBDe0xQWiYDW62VMoITF1g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"287","parent":"279","text":"▶️ Manejo:","guid":"OphYgz88KZulBEYUk8ISRA","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"• Endocarditis infecciosa →\\NATB IV ≥6 semanas ±\\Ncirugía si hay:","guid":"LTJBKCa9H4JMYjYiQJ6DCQ","children":[{"id":"289","parent":"288","text":"• Insuficiencia valvular severa / IC.","guid":"Mwk1FRuy2gZ6HZDVKaOhPA","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"288","text":"• Complicaciones (absceso, extensión perivalvular).","guid":"Mvrz3_i_fAufPoJM1wkFTA","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"288","text":"• Mala respuesta a ATB.","guid":"lNj10iIqXmOMsDB2eHI4Rw","children":[]}]},{"id":"292","parent":"287","text":"• CI antitrombóticos en fase aguda → ⬆ riesgo de hemorragia cerebral.","guid":"BiLrG14_p-n3hG_sGzNZvg","children":[]}]},{"id":"293","parent":"279","text":"▶️ Endocarditis no infecciosa\\N(marántica o Libman-Sacks)","guid":"OLKgLLf-ZLB80EZdEvOPAA","children":[{"id":"294","parent":"293","text":"• Etiologías:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"• Marántica → Asociada a cáncer.","guid":"m5ZCavx91rPMMLr9Ag5qEQ","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"294","text":"• Libman-Sacks → LES.","guid":"rr3WY9dxrSZMwSWjAFJdDw","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"294","text":"• Diagnóstico: Eco-TE ± RM cerebral.","guid":"yjtjrkwE9WYQ88RDn5Pw6A","children":[]}]},{"id":"298","parent":"293","text":"• Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"299","parent":"298","text":"• Marántica (cáncer):","guid":"Ga6wMiew09sWd5hG1IZeXg","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"298","text":"• Heparina o HBPM ± DOACs (evidencia limitada).","guid":"VIer6L8kSNZXEp8hqYDl_g","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"298","text":"• Manejo oncológico.","guid":"OJIldGd4TXT7-e9ReHw0lw","children":[]}]},{"id":"302","parent":"293","text":"• Libman-Sacks\\N(LES):","guid":"0IMLh4xr6mh1DekmmtM51w","children":[{"id":"303","parent":"302","text":"• Heparina o HBPM (preferidos sobre anticoagulación oral).","guid":"23ZSdg8P9o5R8krBId20ug","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"302","text":"• Tratamiento de LES → No está claro si previene ictus.","guid":"f_VoSGQaqsAcj3vnLuZPqw","children":[]},{"id":"305","parent":"302","text":"• Casos seleccionados → Cirugía de reemplazo valvular.","guid":"sdmbWEgAKcJj49xZUfmljQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"306","parent":"256","text":"🔹 Conclusión","guid":"OTXA4Z6fan-gsI4tSLayMw","children":[{"id":"307","parent":"306","text":"▶️ Ictus en válvulas mecánicas → Warfarina (INR según tipo).","guid":"c312KWFCk6fiFXxO3UiSJg","children":[]},{"id":"308","parent":"306","text":"▶️ FA en estenosis mitral → Warfarina preferida.","guid":"BgycMc_vyoB2R9PPd5dRKw","children":[]},{"id":"309","parent":"306","text":"▶️ Endocarditis infecciosa → ATB IV ± cirugía (NO anticoagulación en fase aguda).","guid":"Kr2T1UZboBak9-6b3BFPKw","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"306","text":"▶️ Endocarditis marántica o Libman-Sacks → Heparina/HBPM ± cirugía en casos graves.","guid":"vgAEVsQvx6yIyb_hiGr0wg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"311","parent":"0","text":"🔟 Ictus Isquémico en el Contexto de\\NTumores Cardíacos Izquierdos","guid":"t9ECNzv0GrFDEbgef5cD8w","children":[{"id":"312","parent":"311","text":"▶️ Tumores cardíacos primarios raros pero con potencial embolígeno.","guid":"B1Q6TeOgPXhII-ROE35Pow","children":[]},{"id":"313","parent":"311","text":"▶️ Principales tipos:","guid":"PlP7Mr8kl3JQFL8fUj12EA","children":[{"id":"314","parent":"313","text":"• Mixoma auricular izquierdo → Embolización de trombo y/o tumor.","guid":"V7ErEriLI9-DFcp7xqJkcQ","children":[]},{"id":"315","parent":"313","text":"• Fibroelastoma valvular (aórtico o mitral) → ⬆ riesgo tromboembólico, especialmente si es móvil.","guid":"7T57d_oNrwLmNzE8BkHp6g","children":[]}]},{"id":"316","parent":"311","text":"🔹 Diagnóstico","guid":"RTX-CHNhbR9cNTKSDdWh3A","children":[{"id":"317","parent":"316","text":"▶️ Neuroimagen: Ictus isquémico de origen cardioembólico.","guid":"ncdUxcR6R3aSTCxxELce8w","children":[]},{"id":"318","parent":"316","text":"▶️ Ecocardiografía transesofágica (Eco-TE) → Mejor técnica para visualizar tumores intracardíacos.","guid":"WMhKxD8jZCAKFlqy9SKbxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"319","parent":"311","text":"🔹 Tratamiento","guid":"pInXyXO3l6LjHnYzNQUGvQ","children":[{"id":"320","parent":"319","text":"▶️ Resección quirúrgica del tumor → Primera línea en la mayoría de los casos.","guid":"ErUgoBZ1qNIWVyIidgPjKg","children":[]},{"id":"321","parent":"319","text":"▶️ Antitrombóticos → No hay evidencia clara\\Nsobre qué terapia es mejor, pero suele indicarse:","guid":"MTdlML23wIwYtu637P10oQ","children":[{"id":"322","parent":"321","text":"• Antiagregación o anticoagulación\\Nsegún contexto clínico.","guid":"KDiUvK-E6QC3ZCxsN9QmJQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"323","parent":"311","text":"🔹 Conclusión\\NGeneral","guid":"feslKOQGa-I4PtPjiuM00g","children":[{"id":"324","parent":"323","text":"▶️ El ictus cardioembólico tiene múltiples causas heterogéneas.","guid":"wOb_F-dsc_YgSyANUWccMg","children":[]},{"id":"325","parent":"323","text":"▶️ Identificar el mecanismo específico es clave para la prevención secundaria.","guid":"q8XB81c0w-6om2XaZdjUPQ","children":[]},{"id":"326","parent":"323","text":"▶️ El manejo varía según la etiología → desde anticoagulación hasta cirugía en casos seleccionados.","guid":"_66EDyoz8QUC82aD17ELXw","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":326,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"Continuum. Diagnóstico y manejo del Ictus cardioembolico-2025","id":"map_272","resolved_references":[]}